{
  "stem": "22447.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They signed the road to go into Bayeux, but they didn't sign it to going out.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] So everybody's going around in a circle.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So we got rid of that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And then, the roads got very quiet.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "The traffic went to a trickle, and there wasn't much doing.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So I stopped the driver, I said, where's all the traffic gone to?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Are they going somewhere else?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "He said, don't you know?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "He says, that Mulberry Harbour, the wind had broken it, and there was a terrible gale out there, they can't land a thing.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "The medical supplies and food was being rationed.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And ammunition was being rationed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "He said, they can't-- they can't land a thing.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "They don't know what to do.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Because we had just landed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "If you're not getting supplies, then how long can you stay there?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "So Montgomery went down to the beaches.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "That's what I-- here, you had to have a proper field commander on the spot.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "It was no good directing the war from the War Office.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Like in the-- when the war first started, if a German plane went over France, you had to find a War Office, if you can shoot it down.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] So he went down to the beaches.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He surveyed the situation, he said, unload the ships.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Whatever gets through, gets through.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Some of them didn't-- the waves turned them over.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, we didn't interfere with them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, we had the feeling we were well-received.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It didn't take long before the children come around.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Say, have you got chocolate for mama, have you got soap for papas?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We said no, but we've got sweets for your sister.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[LAUGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No-- no, we was on duty 24 hours a day.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then we pushed through, we was going through France.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
